                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 210.) I took the prisoner—I found these six brushes in his cap, this other on his person, and twelve duplicates of brushes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was not in the prosecutor's employ, but that of his daughter—she said he had nothing to do with it—these brushes were my own manufacture at the time of my starting in business, eighteen months ago.</p>
